      "content": {
        "title": "About Me",
        "data": {},
        "html": "<p>Creative and user-centered <strong>UX Designer</strong> with 7 years of experience crafting delightful digital experiences. Passionate about accessibility, inclusive design, and bridging the gap between user needs and business goals. Led design for products used by 20M+ users, with expertise in design systems, user research, and prototyping. Believer that great design is invisible – it just works.</p>"
      }
